CONTENTICIOUS

Contenticious is a simple way to build a nice little website from
Markdown content.


PREREQUISITES

    - File::Copy::Recursive 0.38
    - Mojolicious 2.4
    - Mojolicious::Plugin::Subdispatch 0.02
    - Mojolicious::Plugin::RelativeUrlFor 0.01
    - Text::Markdown 1.000031


INSTALLATION

Download the dist tarball or clone the git repository and execute the
following standard procedure:

    $ perl Makefile.PL
    $ make
    $ make test
    $ make install

It's possible to use this module from inside of its dist directory without
installation.


DOCUMENTATION

After installation you can access the main documentation with this command:

    $ perldoc Contenticious

It's possible to view the same file without installing Contenticious:
https://github.com/memowe/contenticious/blob/master/lib/Contenticious.pod


